item.description: An informal meeting where we'll talk about our situations and, for those who have been to previous meetings, report on our promises. These are promises made to ourselves but heard by others. There is a strength in telling other people what you intend to do. Of course you don't have to commit to anything. Come to share your situation with others who understand (all too well). Get advice from people who've been in your shoes. And, if you think it might help, find a clutter buddy.
item.how_to_find_us: We'll have a sign saying Metrowest P & C at the table
item.name: Make commitments and meet them, with a little help from our friends
